# Quick guide / 快速说明:
# - This is the production-oriented example.
# - For bilingual explanations of the variables, read `docs/ENVIRONMENT.md`.
# - Do not enable `MORPHEUS_ENABLE_UNTRUSTED_SCRIPTS` unless you intentionally want user JS execution.

